  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, I'm Miss Maya. I'm a tea person — it's my evening comfort. How was your day?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hi Maya, nice to meet you. I'm more of a coffee guy, but tea is okay too. My day was busy, working on a project deadline. How about you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it. Coffee makes you alert, tea makes me calm — both work. You mentioned a project deadline. Was it stressful?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "A bit, but manageable. We met the deadline, so I'm relieved. By the way, I'm going for a cricket match this weekend. Excited!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That’s great — meeting deadlines is always a win. Cricket matches are exciting! Which team are you supporting?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "India vs Pakistan, obviously! It's always a high-voltage match. I might watch it with some naan and chai. Want to join virtually? 😄"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "India vs Pakistan is always intense — classic rivalry! Naan and chai sound perfect for the mood. I’ll be a virtual cheering fan. What time is the match?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "7:30 PM IST. You'll have to stay up a bit late, but it's worth it! 🚨 India's got a good chance this time, I think. Will you root for them or play neutral? 😄"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I’ll root for India — no question! The spirit of the match is half the fun. I get the excitement, it's a big one. Enjoy your naan and chai!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks Maya! It'll be better with good company, even if virtual. 🙌 I'll make sure to update you after the match — India or Pakistan, we'll chat about it. Now, I should get back to work. Talk to you later! 😊"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You're very welcome! Company makes everything better, even virtual. Have a great work session — I'll be here for your update later! 🙌"
    }
  ],
